google.description: When their normal lifestyle is threatened by their business, a senseless tragedy and a shady ex-lover, Ramsey and Keilah Stone, the owners of the Stone-Chase Protection Agency, must make some difficult decisions to protect their family. Original.
google.title: Precious Stones
